title: Ravens-Cowboys TuNF Recap: Dez Bryant tests positive for COVID-19 pregame (Football 12/9)
description:
Another Tuesday night treat, if you want to call it that. More football on unusual days and to break down Ravens-Cowboys, Will Brinson is joined by John Breech and (Dallas fan) Jared Dubin. The guys tackle a poor showing from the Cowboys and what the future holds the rest of the year and beyond this year for the organization. They also analyze Baltimore's postseason chances as well as the weird situation pregame as Dez Bryant was ruled out after a very late positive COVID-19 test result.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
